{"word":"φιμόω","slug":"φιμόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>φιμόω</el></b> [<el>φιμός</el> ‘muzzle’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘shut a mouth with a tightening device’, <b>to muzzle <a href='B:530 9:9'>1 Cor 9:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:610 5:18'>1 Ti 5:18</a>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fig.\">fig.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to cease making a sound’, <b>to silence, muzzle, gag <a href='B:470 22:12'>Mt 22:12</a>, <a href='B:470 22:34'>34</a>; <a href='B:480 1:25'>Mk 1:25</a>; <a href='B:480 4:39'>4:39</a>; <a href='B:490 4:35'>Lk 4:35</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:φιλόφρων\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:φιμώθητι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}